---
description: Enforce feature branch workflow and protect main/master
alwaysApply: true
---

# Feature Branch Workflow

- Never commit directly on `main` or `master`.
- Never push directly to `main` or `master`.
- If currently on `main` or `master`, create a feature branch first:
  - `git switch -c <type>/<short-name>`
- Push feature branches and merge through pull requests.
- If a user explicitly asks to bypass this policy, warn about risk and require explicit confirmation before proceeding.
